{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DataTransfer.types","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/types","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API\">HTML Drag and Drop API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer\"><code>DataTransfer</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/DataTransfer\"><code>DataTransfer()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/dropEffect\"><code>dropEffect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/effectAllowed\"><code>effectAllowed</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/files\"><code>files</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/items\"><code>items</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozCursor\"><code>mozCursor</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozItemCount\"><code>mozItemCount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozSourceNode\"><code>mozSourceNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozUserCancelled\"><code>mozUserCancelled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>types</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/addElement\"><code>addElement()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/clearData\"><code>clearData()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/getData\"><code>getData()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozClearDataAt\"><code>mozClearDataAt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozGetDataAt\"><code>mozGetDataAt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozSetDataAt\"><code>mozSetDataAt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/mozTypesAt\"><code>mozTypesAt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/setData\"><code>setData()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/setDragImage\"><code>setDragImage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for HTML Drag and Drop API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItem\"><code>DataTransferItem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItemList\"><code>DataTransferItemList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DragEvent\"><code>DragEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"返回值","id":"返回值","isH3":true,"query":"api.DataTransfer.types","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/types/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>DataTransfer.types</code></strong>&nbsp;是只读属性。它返回一个我们在<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">dragstart (en-US)</a></code>事件中设置的拖动数据格式 (如&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\" title=\"字符串\"><code>字符串</code></a>) 的数组。 格式顺序与拖动操作中包含的数据顺序相同。&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>这些格式是指定数据类型或格式的 Unicode 字符串，通常由 MIME 类型给出。 一些非 MIME 类型的值是由于历史遗留原因（例如“text”）而特殊设置的。</p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\"><var>dataTransfer</var>.types;\n</pre>\n\n\n\n<p>拖动操作中使用的数据格式数组。每种格式都是<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\" title=\"字符串\"><code>字符串</code></a>类型。如果拖动操作不包含数据，则此数组列表将为空。如果拖动操作中包含任何文件，则其中一个类型将是<code>Files。</code></p>\n\n\n\n<p>这个例子展示<code>types</code>和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/items\" title=\"items\"><code>items</code></a> 属性的用法</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\n&lt;html lang=en&gt;\n&lt;title&gt;Examples of DataTransfer.{types,items} properties&lt;/title&gt;\n&lt;meta content=\"width=device-width\"&gt;\n&lt;style&gt;\n  div {\n    margin: 0em;\n    padding: 2em;\n  }\n  #target {\n    border: 1px solid black;\n  }\n&lt;/style&gt;\n&lt;script&gt;\nfunction dragstart_handler(ev) {\n console.log(\"dragStart: target.id = \" + ev.target.id);\n&nbsp;// 将这个元素的 id 添加到 drag 载荷中，\n // 以便 drop 事件知道将哪个元素添加到其树中。\n ev.dataTransfer.setData(\"text/plain\", ev.target.id);\n ev.dataTransfer.effectAllowed = \"move\";\n}\n\nfunction drop_handler(ev) {\n console.log(\"drop: target.id = \" + ev.target.id);\n ev.preventDefault();\n // 得到目标的 id 并且将移动的元素添加到目标 DOM 中\n var data = ev.dataTransfer.getData(\"text\");\n ev.target.appendChild(document.getElementById(data));\n&nbsp;// 打印每种格式类型\n if (ev.dataTransfer.types != null) {\n   for (var i=0; i &lt; ev.dataTransfer.types.length; i++) {\n     console.log(\"... types[\" + i + \"] = \" + ev.dataTransfer.types[i]);\n   }\n }\n&nbsp;// 打印每个 item 的“kind”和“type”属性值\n if (ev.dataTransfer.items != null) {\n   for (var i=0; i &lt; ev.dataTransfer.items.length; i++) {\n     console.log(\"... items[\" + i + \"].kind = \" + ev.dataTransfer.items[i].kind + \" ; type = \" + ev.dataTransfer.items[i].type);\n   }\n }\n}\n\nfunction dragover_handler(ev) {\n console.log(\"dragOver\");\n ev.preventDefault();\n // 设置 dropEffect 属性值为 move\n ev.dataTransfer.dropEffect = \"move\"\n}\n&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;body&gt;\n&lt;h1&gt;Examples of &lt;code&gt;DataTransfer&lt;/code&gt;.{&lt;code&gt;types&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;items&lt;/code&gt;} properties&lt;/h1&gt;\n &lt;ul&gt;\n   &lt;li id=\"i1\" ondragstart=\"dragstart_handler(event);\" draggable=\"true\"&gt;Drag Item 1 to the Drop Zone&lt;/li&gt;\n   &lt;li id=\"i2\" ondragstart=\"dragstart_handler(event);\" draggable=\"true\"&gt;Drag Item 2 to the Drop Zone&lt;/li&gt;\n &lt;/ul&gt;\n &lt;div id=\"target\" ondrop=\"drop_handler(event);\" ondragover=\"dragover_handler(event);\"&gt;Drop Zone&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</pre>\n\n\n\n<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范文档</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">说明</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#dom-datatransfer-types\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">types</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/editing.html#dom-datatransfer-types\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">types</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p></p><ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API\">Drag and drop</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API/Drag_operations\">Drag Operations</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API/Recommended_drag_types\">Recommended Drag Types</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API/Multiple_items\">Dragging and Dropping Multiple Items</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://codepen.io/tech_query/pen/MqGgap\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DataTransfer test - Paste or Drag</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"DataTransfer.types 是只读属性。它返回一个我们在dragstart (en-US)事件中设置的拖动数据格式 (如 字符串) 的数组。 格式顺序与拖动操作中包含的数据顺序相同。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DataTransfer.types","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DataTransfer.types","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/datatransfer/types","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/datatransfer/types/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer","title":"DataTransfer"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer/types","title":"DataTransfer.types"}],"pageTitle":"DataTransfer.types - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}